PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the RED PHEASANT BAND surrenders, for an indefinite term, some 3,024 hectares of land on Red Pheasant Indian Reserve No. 108 in Saskatchewan, for the purpose of allowing the Crown to issue leases, licences and permits to third parties for oil and gas exploration and development.
